- Yeah, she is.

151
00:13:48.703 --> 00:13:50.704
Next to you.

152
00:13:51.247 --> 00:13:55.751
Tell you what, I look at her, though, and
I cannot help but think about little Tonya.

153
00:13:57.420 --> 00:13:59.087
