Just curious.

198
00:17:20.665 --> 00:17:22.999
Um, Miss Ethel...

199
00:17:23.167 --> 00:17:27.379
refresh my recollection, how long
were you and Lucien together for exactly?

200
00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:28.755
We were never together.

201
00:17:28.923 --> 00:17:31.007
I was his secretary for 20 years.

202
00:17:31.175 --> 00:17:32.968
Come on, old girl.

203
00:17:33.136 --> 00:17:35.637
- You can tell us, you know.
- He was your boyfriend.

204
00:17:35.805 --> 00:17:39.725
I am an upstanding, God-fearing,
respectable Southern woman...

205
00:17:39.892 --> 00:17:44.020
