who has been happily married for 27 years.

206
00:17:44.188 --> 00:17:48.108
And I have never had
or ever will have any boyfriend.

207
00:17:48.276 --> 00:17:49.776
And if I did...

208
00:17:49.944 --> 00:17:55.031
