that old pickled scoundrel Lucien Wilbanks.

209
00:17:59.412 --> 00:18:02.122
She did him. Oh, yeah, a lot.

210
00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:11.173
All right, Billy Ray, step on back.

211
00:18:11.966 --> 00:18:14.259
Come on out. Willard.

212
00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:19.181
All right, boys, today's your big day.

213
00:18:19.348 --> 00:18:21.224
