Jake? Jake? Are you hurt?
Jake, what happened to you?

223
00:20:46.704 --> 00:20:49.539
Jake, honey, are you okay?
What happened to you?

224
00:20:49.707 --> 00:20:53.001
What is this? What is going on with you?
What happened?

225
00:20:53.169 --> 00:20:55.045
Jake, baby.

226
00:20:56.047 --> 00:20:58.256
What happened?

227
00:21:31.415 --> 00:21:33.541
Okay, okay.

228
00:21:49.642 --> 00:21:50.684
See you, Gwen.

229
00:22:04.782 --> 00:22:06.658
Is the sheriff gonna make a statement?

230
00:22:06.826 --> 00:22:08.618
He might, he might not. I don't know.

231
00:22:08.786 --> 00:22:11.413
- Is it first-degree murder?
- I'm not sure yet.

232
00:22:11.580 --> 00:22:13.581
What happened?
Can you tell us something?

233
00:22:13.749 --> 00:22:16.960
- Sheriff, will you give us a statement.
- I got no comment. No comment.

234
