Hey. Hey, Jake.
Hey, Jake, Carl Lee said you'd be coming.

235
00:22:20.256 --> 00:22:22.549
- Sir, are you an attorney?
- Are you an attorney?

236
00:22:22.717 --> 00:22:26.094
