240
00:22:59.962 --> 00:23:03.465
I ain't had nothing against them boys
till they messed with my baby.

241
00:23:04.383 --> 00:23:08.595
And I feel sorry for their mamas
and their daddies, but...

242
00:23:09.305 --> 00:23:11.264
