247
00:23:30.451 --> 00:23:32.744
There's gonna be a preliminary hearing.

248
00:23:32.912 --> 00:23:35.205
Probably tomorrow.

249
00:23:35.664 --> 00:23:37.832
After that, Buckley will push
for a fast trial.

250
00:23:38.834 --> 00:23:39.959
Who's Buckley?

251
00:23:40.127 --> 00:23:41.628
Rufus Buckley.

252
00:23:41.796 --> 00:23:42.837
District attorney.

253
00:23:43.005 --> 00:23:47.008
He's mean, he's ambitious, and he's
gonna eat this up because of the publicity.

254
00:23:47.176 --> 00:23:48.968
But you've done beat him, ain't you?

255
