291
00:26:06.273 --> 00:26:09.317
- Guy would be a fool if he didn't.
- Why's that?

292
00:26:09.818 --> 00:26:10.944
Why?

293
00:26:11.111 --> 00:26:13.446
Should we tell our young,
uninformed law clerk...

294
00:26:13.614 --> 00:26:15.782
the reality of jurisprudence
in this county?

295
00:26:15.950 --> 00:26:20.078
