311
00:27:02.579 --> 00:27:06.082
- I believe that's Dewars.
- Keep that old drunk on the sidelines.

312
00:27:06.250 --> 00:27:07.333
Yeah, get me Sam.

313
00:27:07.501 --> 00:27:09.252
And, gentlemen?

314
00:27:10.546 --> 00:27:13.756
No mistakes.
This is the one we've been waiting for.

315
00:27:14.550 --> 00:27:17.385
Justifiable homicide will never hold up.

316
00:27:17.553 --> 00:27:20.179
