321
00:27:35.404 --> 00:27:38.906
then you'll get an all-white jury
and you'll lose.

322
00:27:39.366 --> 00:27:40.825
Thank you for the encouragement.

323
00:27:40.993 --> 00:27:45.913
Well, bear in mind that Mr. Hailey
