Now, that's a strange case.

332
00:28:14.360 --> 00:28:15.985
Yeah.

333
00:28:17.780 --> 00:28:19.989
I could use your help.

334
00:28:22.534 --> 00:28:25.411
The sons of bitches decertified me, Jake.

335
00:28:25.579 --> 00:28:28.956
I swore I will never
enter another courtroom ever.

336
00:28:29.124 --> 00:28:32.543
Lucien, you're the best lawyer
I've ever seen.

337
00:28:32.711 --> 00:28:35.713
Now, I know how much it hurt
when they took your license away...

338
00:28:35.881 --> 00:28:38.341
but they can't take your mind
unless you let them.

339
00:28:39.635 --> 00:28:40.843
Good speech.

340
00:28:41.011 --> 00:28:43.137
Well, I had a good teacher.

341
00:28:43.305 --> 00:28:46.265
