383
00:31:02.611 --> 00:31:06.572
I intend to show the men and women of the
South to look past color and see the truth.

384
00:31:06.740 --> 00:31:11.160
That here in the South— In the new South,
justice is and will be colorblind.

385
00:31:13.747 --> 00:31:16.290
- Impressive. Honey, that was really good.
- Hmm?

386
00:31:16.458 --> 00:31:18.834
- Isn't Daddy smart?
- Mm-hm.

387
00:31:19.002 --> 00:31:20.461
Yeah. Brigance.

388
00:31:20.629 --> 00:31:21.796
- Mm-hm.
- That was great.

389
00:31:21.964 --> 00:31:24.048
Yeah. No, we just saw it.

390
00:31:24.216 --> 00:31:25.550
All right, Harry Rex. Yeah.

391
00:31:25.717 --> 00:31:26.926
Baby, I'm proud of you.

392
00:31:28.303 --> 00:31:29.637
- Good stuff, huh?
- Mm-hm.

393
00:31:29.805 --> 00:31:32.014
- You hear this?
- Put it on speakerphone.

394
00:31:32.182 --> 00:31:34.058
Don't be gross.

395
00:31:34.434 --> 00:31:37.562
- Ahem. F. Lee Bailey's office.
- Brigance.

396
00:31:37.729 --> 00:31:42.483
You nigger-loving son-of-a-bitch,
