You're a mother, I'm a father.

400
00:31:51.493 --> 00:31:54.287
We all have families. Who wouldn't?

401
00:31:54.454 --> 00:31:56.789
Don't presume the district attorney
is insensitive.

402
00:31:56.957 --> 00:31:59.000
But the people
of the state of Mississippi...

403
00:31:59.167 --> 00:32:01.752
entrusted this office
to uphold the law of the land.

404
00:32:01.920 --> 00:32:05.131
Our society cannot condone men
who take the law into their own hands.

405
00:32:05.299 --> 00:32:06.549
No matter the circumstance.

406
00:32:06.717 --> 00:32:09.385
If you get a conviction,
will you ask for the gas chamber?

407
00:32:09.553 --> 00:32:12.179
Yes, I will seek the death penalty
for Mr. Hailey.

408
00:32:12.347 --> 00:32:14.181
What do you think of Mr. Brigance?

409
00:32:14.349 --> 00:32:16.392
Isn't that boy still in law school?

410
00:32:16.560 --> 00:32:18.644
Say hey to your husband for me, Kim.
That's all.

411
00:32:33.368 --> 00:32:36.203
Hey, Cora Mae, don't you worry.
Hey, Wayne, how are you?

412
00:32:36.371 --> 00:32:37.955
Good luck.

413
00:32:39.541 --> 00:32:42.585
You plead him guilty today, I'll ask for life.
Otherwise, he dies.

414
00:32:42.753 --> 00:32:46.339
You drop your case now, and I won't
bury you before the entire county, Rufus.

415
00:32:47.799 --> 00:32:49.008
All rise.

416
00:32:50.844 --> 00:32:54.513
Court is in session.
The Honorable Omar Noose presiding.

417
00:32:54.681 --> 00:32:57.058
Good afternoon, citizens.

418
00:32:59.144 --> 00:33:00.728
Be seated.

419
00:33:00.896 --> 00:33:02.480
Counsel.

420
00:33:02.648 --> 00:33:04.231
And you, sir.

421
00:33:04.399 --> 00:33:06.901
- Are you Carl Lee Hailey?
- Yes, sir.

422
00:33:07.069 --> 00:33:11.072
Uh, Mr. Hailey, I am holding
a copy of an indictment returned...

423
00:33:11.239 --> 00:33:14.742
by the grand jury of Mississippi
presenting that:

424
00:33:14.910 --> 00:33:19.622
"Carl Lee Hailey did murder Billy Ray Cobb,
a human being...

425
00:33:19.790 --> 00:33:22.625
and James Lewis Willard,
a human being...

426
00:33:22.793 --> 00:33:26.837
and did attempt to kill Dwayne Looney,
a peace officer...

427
00:33:27.005 --> 00:33:30.049
against the peace and dignity
of the state of Mississippi."

428
00:33:30.467 --> 00:33:32.927
Now, do you understand
the charges against you?

429
00:33:33.387 --> 00:33:35.971
- Yes, sir.
- How do you wish to plead?

430
00:33:38.600 --> 00:33:39.850
Not guilty, Your Honor.

431
00:33:41.061 --> 00:33:44.480
The defense enters a plea of not guilty
by reason of insanity, Your Honor.

432
00:33:44.648 --> 00:33:46.649
Your trial is set for July 22.

433
00:33:46.817 --> 00:33:51.112
All pretrial motions and matters
should be filed no later than July 8.

434
00:33:51.279 --> 00:33:52.738
- Is there anything further?
- Yes.

435
00:33:52.906 --> 00:33:55.032
Your Honor,
in response to the insanity plea...

436
00:33:55.200 --> 00:33:58.285
the state requests the defendant
be examined by its own doctors.

437
00:33:58.453 --> 00:33:59.453
Request granted.

438
00:33:59.621 --> 00:34:02.748
Additionally,
the state opposes any request for bail.

439
00:34:02.916 --> 00:34:04.834
Your Honor,
we haven't yet asked for bail.

440
00:34:05.001 --> 00:34:07.962
Now, Governor Buckley cannot oppose
a request until one is made.

441
00:34:08.130 --> 00:34:10.005
He should've learned that in law school.

442
00:34:10.173 --> 00:34:13.759
Your Honor, even Mr. Brigance's
meager legal experience...

443
00:34:13.927 --> 00:34:18.097
should've taught him two things.
One, I have not been elected governor yet.

444
00:34:18.265 --> 00:34:21.142
And number two,
he is required to request bail.

445
00:34:21.309 --> 00:34:22.935
The state opposes any such request.

446
00:34:23.103 --> 00:34:26.480
In the future, why don't we just wait
till he makes the request, huh?

447
00:34:26.732 --> 00:34:27.940
Thank you, Your Honor.

448
00:34:28.108 --> 00:34:30.651
- Your Honor, we would like to request bail.
- Denied.

449
00:34:31.778 --> 00:34:34.196
I have never allowed bail
in a capital-murder case...

450
00:34:34.364 --> 00:34:37.700
and don't feel
that an exception is called for today.

451
00:34:37.868 --> 00:34:38.993
Good enough.

452
00:34:39.161 --> 00:34:41.245
We will be filing for a change of venue.

453
00:34:41.413 --> 00:34:42.830
I anticipated this.

454
00:34:42.998 --> 00:34:45.583
Let me save you some time,
Mr. Brigance.

455
00:34:45.751 --> 00:34:47.251
Your motion is denied.

456
00:34:47.419 --> 00:34:49.336
Your Honor, we have not yet filed.

457
00:34:49.504 --> 00:34:53.382
We are simply indicating
our intent to file in writing by letting you—

458
00:34:53.550 --> 00:34:55.843
I said, request denied.

459
00:34:56.553 --> 00:34:57.928
Your Honor...

460
00:34:58.096 --> 00:35:01.307
how can you summarily deny
this request?

461
00:35:01.475 --> 00:35:04.810
