cannot receive a fair trial here.

462
00:35:04.978 --> 00:35:07.438
- Now, we feel—
- That's enough. Sidebar.

463
00:35:07.606 --> 00:35:09.023
Your Honor, we have a right—

464
00:35:09.191 --> 00:35:12.067
Mr. Brigance.

465
00:35:12.235 --> 00:35:15.780
I will not tolerate grandstanding
in my courtroom.

466
00:35:23.789 --> 00:35:25.790
Get back to work.

467
00:35:26.625 --> 00:35:29.543
Excellent technique, counselor.

468
00:35:41.515 --> 00:35:42.556
Your Honor.

469
00:35:42.808 --> 00:35:46.393
We feel it would be remiss not to tell you
that in State v. Johnson...

470
00:35:46.561 --> 00:35:48.187
and State v. Fisher...

471
00:35:48.355 --> 00:35:50.189
both in 1985...

472
00:35:50.357 --> 00:35:53.025
failure to properly consider
a change of venue...

473
00:35:53.193 --> 00:35:56.612
has been a reversible decision on appeal
to the state supreme court.

474
00:35:58.073 --> 00:36:02.952
No... No trial judge
likes his rulings overturned.

475
00:36:03.119 --> 00:36:09.291
I guess you get to submit that brief after all.
Have it on my desk by Tuesday morning.

476
00:36:09.751 --> 00:36:12.419
Mr. Hailey, you are hereby ordered...

477
00:36:12.587 --> 00:36:17.675
to remain in custody of
the Madison County sheriff until trial.

478
00:36:17.843 --> 00:36:18.884
