487
00:36:57.632 --> 00:36:59.383
Mine too.

488
00:37:01.845 --> 00:37:03.637
All right, when do I get the rest?

489
00:37:04.097 --> 00:37:07.349
Them folks over at the bank,
they won't loan me no money on my house.

490
00:37:07.517 --> 00:37:11.896
